text: Phoebemima albomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2008. It is known from Bolivia.BioLib.cz - Phoebemima albomaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2008
title: Phoebemima albomaculata
